<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>BodyCorp | Segurança Inteligente</title>

	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

	<style>
		body {
			background-color: #000;
			color: #fff;
			font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
		}

		/* NAVBAR */
		.custom-navbar {
			background: #000 !important; /* Preto sólido */
			border-bottom: 1px solid #0aff0a50;
		}

		.navbar-brand {
			color: #0aff0a !important;
		}

		.nav-link {
			color: #0aff0a !important;
			font-weight: 500;
			transition: 0.3s;
		}

			.nav-link:hover {
				color: #ffffff !important;
			}

		/* HERO */
		.hero-section {
			height: 100vh;
			background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537498425277-c283d32ef9db?w=1200') center/cover no-repeat;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			text-align: center;
			position: relative;
		}

			.hero-section::after {
				content: "";
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				background: rgba(0,0,0,0.65);
			}

		.hero-content {
			position: relative;
			z-index: 10;
		}

		.hero-title {
			font-size: 3.3rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			color: #0aff0a;
			text-shadow: 0 0 15px #0aff0a;
		}

		.hero-subtitle {
			max-width: 850px;
			margin: 15px auto;
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.hero-btn {
			background-color: #0aff0a;
			border: none;
			color: #000;
			font-weight: 700;
			border-radius: 10px;
			padding: 12px 30px;
			transition: .3s;
			box-shadow: 0 0 15px #0aff0a;
		}

			.hero-btn:hover {
				background-color: #00cc00;
				box-shadow: 0 0 25px #0aff0a;
				transform: translateY(-3px);
			}

		/* SEÇÕES */
		.info-section {
			padding: 100px 15px;
			background: #061306;
			border-top: solid 2px #0aff0a20;
			border-bottom: solid 2px #0aff0a20;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.info-title {
			font-size: 2.3rem;
			color: #0aff0a;
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.info-text {
			max-width: 770px;
			margin: 20px auto;
			font-size: 1.15rem;
			color: #d9ffd9;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>

	<header>
		<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm fixed-top custom-navbar">
			<div class="container-fluid">

				<a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="#home">BodyCorp</a>

				<button class="navbar-toggler bg-success" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#mainNav">
					<span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
				</button>

				<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="mainNav">
					<ul class="navbar-nav ms-3">
						<!-- Alinhado à esquerda -->
						<li class="nav-item mx-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#home">Home</a></li>
						<li class="nav-item mx-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#sobre">Sobre a Empresa</a></li>
						<li class="nav-item mx-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#contato">Contato</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>

			</div>
		</nav>
	</header>

	<section class="hero-section" id="home">
		<div class="container hero-content">
			<h1 class="hero-title">Tecnologia que protege quem move o mundo</h1>
			<p class="hero-subtitle">Soluções inteligentes utilizando IA e sensores avançados para prevenção de riscos e cuidados com a saúde no trabalho.</p>
			<a href="#sobre" class="hero-btn">Saiba Mais</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="info-section" id="sobre">
		<h2 class="info-title">Por que a BodyCorp?</h2>
		<p class="info-text">
			Combinamos sensores de alta precisão e Inteligência Artificial para monitorar movimentos, prevenir lesões e promover mais segurança.
			Nascemos para proteger quem move o mundo com esforço e dedicação. 💪
		</p>
	</section>


	<section class="info-section" id="contato">
		<h2 class="info-title">Fale Conosco</h2>
		<p class="info-text">Quer saber mais sobre nossas soluções?</p>
		<p class="info-text fw-bold">✉ contato@bodycorp.com</p>
	</section>

</body>
</html>
